3.text: Arul : Hello Hasan, how was your weekend? Hasan: It was great! We went to the Royal Nature Park. Arul : Really? What did you see there? Hasan: There were many beautiful flowers and different kinds of trees. I took a lot of pictures too. Arul : Could you bring them next week? I'd love to see them. Hasan: Do you know that there are some people who pluck these beautiful flowers, write on trees and throw food all over the park? Arul : That is very bad. They should not do it. Hasan: Yes, that's true. Arul : What else did you do? Hasan: We sat under a large tree and had our lunch. Arul : That must have been wonderful. Hasan: Yes, it was, and we did not forget to put all the leftover food into the garbage bins. Arul : I would love to go to the National Park too. Hasan: You should, and if you like, I will come with you. Arul : Thank you, Hasan. That will be nice.
